      <agency>Novartis</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Novartis</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Bipolar disorder is a psychiatric illness with clinical characteristics of mixed mania,
      grandiose delusions, and suicidality. This study will investigate the efficacy a safety of
      oxcarbazepine in the treatment of patients with bipolar disorder type I or II.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
